OL,3,COldest person in the North West
OL,4,Ccelebrates 112th birthday
OL,6,FA woman who was born before the
OL,7,Foutbreak of World War One has
OL,8,Fcelebrated her 112th birthday.
OL,10,FMarjorie Hodnett Aylward -
OL,11,Faffectionately known as Aunt Marj - is
OL,12,Fthe oldest person in the North West
OL,13,Fand the fifth oldest person in the UK.
OL,15,FShe said her life motto is: "Do all
OL,16,Fthe good you can, to all the people
OL,17,Fyou can, in all the ways you can, as
OL,18,Flong as ever you can."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
