OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775135469
OL,3,COldest person in the North West
OL,4,Ccelebrates 112th birthday
OL,6,FAunt Marj celebrated her birthday with
OL,7,Ffriends family and staff at the care
OL,8,Fhome where she lives in Formby.
OL,10,FShe received a card from the King and
OL,11,FQueen, congratulating her on her 112
OL,12,Fbirthday - but it is not the first
OL,13,Fcard she has received from a royal.
OL,15,FShe said: "When you reach 105, you get
OL,16,Fone automatically."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
