OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775135469
OL,3,COldest person in the North West
OL,4,Ccelebrates 112th birthday
OL,6,FThe card read: "We are pleased to
OL,7,Fknown of you 112th birthday, and we
OL,8,Fsend you our warmest congratulations
OL,9,Fon a wonderful celebration. Charles
OL,10,Fand Camilla."
OL,12,FAunt Marj has lived through 25 Prime
OL,13,FMinisters, five monarchs and two world
OL,14,Fwars.
OL,16,FShe recalled being held in her
OL,17,Fmother's arms in 1916, watching men in
OL,18,Fa Zeppelin Airship throw bombs during
OL,19,FGerman air raids on the UK.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
